reviews.review_text: The guy who was working at the drive thru window tonight November 17 at 12:07 am was super friendly. By far the best customer service I ve had at any McDonald s!

I rarely post reviews but couldn t resist posting this one.There is this one employee working at this location, I believe his name is -Dharampreet, he is such a gem! He never fails to acknowledge the delivery drivers waiting to pick up orders. He always greets all customers with a smile. This store is so lucky to have an employee like him. He is a great asset to the team.
They ve had great service and didn t wait to long. Food was good too and wonderful service
Paris gave me great customer service. Mcd did improve alot in all these years, actually all the staff was amazing. Thank u guys for turning a bad day in a good one :) Thanks Paris
After visiting this location recently theyve managed to flip my 1 star review into a 5 star review. Keep up the great work

A lady infont of us seemed to have issues with ordering and the person taking her order asked her to come to the window and helped her further with her order. She kindly took my order and was satisfied with the order.
Fast sumtimes night timee around 9pm-11pm the drive gets crazy like everyones gets the munchies around those times
Best McDonalds in the area imho. Appreciate the attention to detail as my orders are always accurate, made fresh and served fast by friendly staff.
Its McDonalds, what can I say !? Lol delicious when you dislike yourself
Close to my place.. sometimes they dont have the ice cream machine working.
Always fresh food..including fries which is great. The area attracts some questionable people so I wouldnt eat in the restaurant unless it was necessary. Great staff and service.

Good location, bus stop for the frequent # 319 bus is right outside. Like this large location, as I can quickly catch the bus to ride on 72nd avenue. Rumoured to have many homeless or needy men visit here in previous years, before renovations. The renovation to this location was a very successful upgrade, years ago. Kiosk here to order with, my preference. The orders from delivery drivers working for  Skip The Dishes  was quite huge last time I visited.
One of the best McDonalds

Typical McDonalds in almost everything. They close the dining area at night but I did a order through the app and they let me walk up in the drive thru which Ive never had luck doing that before. Maybe it was because I ordered in the app or just because the staff is so nice

I went to this location staff was really friendly apparently they were not serving chicken muffin at 12 so a manager came to me and explained about the different between junior chicken and i got my meal and left happily. That manager was really comfortable and happy to talk with.

Bro its not easy to make an order in 2 mins. Ev eryone does mistake but they dont want to unsatisfy their customers. If you talk with them politely you will definitely get your oder and sometimes your money back. thank you hope you all understand.
This McDonalds staff seems to work hard to maintain the building. Very good space for dining in very clean and friendly staff. Radha and Rosa like staff work beyond their duty to satisfy customers.

Really appreciated the way they treat customers always ready to help and always serve well done food especially late night staff really deserve appreciation as I just had a visit there last night and my experience is awesome....

So nice place enjoyed a lot . The staffs are so nice and humble .The manager Sanchit is very helpful , he helped us in all possible ways in deciding the hot coffee and also offers us free coffee card.
My favourite store to eat at! Always clean and great service, staff is friendly and very helpful. Good for eating in and drive thru. Food is always fresh and prepared perfectly! Amazing store.

I visited 72nd king george mcd My kid was forcing me to get him fountain drink but I was trying to get him smoothie or juice. There was girl i think she is manager she anyhow managed him to get juice instead. She was so generous and childish to get over the kids. She made my day when she gave a free toy to baby. I would love visiting there soon.
They are so nice, I love the brownie cookies
My son works here. Quick meal

This is the only McDonalds where I have been attended the best and always had fresh fries no matter what. For all the food lovers out there this is a total recommendation from the experience of past 10 years. Cheers! Enjoy your McDonalds....................

I loved this place! !   I went through drive thru and placed my order with this young man he was very polite and also generous!! When I wanted only 1 poutine he gave me 2!! I asked him that I only wanted 1 but then he just smiled and said that customers always should be EXTRA happy. And I was!!!!
Its not bad! Parking is easy and they just opened 10 spots for mobile ordering. Drive through is standard too.
Superb service really satisfied with drive thru service and delivery service late night ... Just awesome experience must visit.
Whole overnight staff is great at dealing with customers and orders. They are very co-operating and polite behaviour
I did a Mobile Order for lunch. Drove up thru to driver thru and it was easy peasy. They speedy and my food didnt look rushed to make. I like going to this location  on 72nd and King George.
I went to this location on last Friday. The guy named Sagar helped me. He was very helpful and friendly. Thanks Sagar, Keep up your good work

Thank you so much to Macdonalds on 72nd and king George  for being so compassionate and caring to frontline workers.  Special thanks to Radhna Singh and Radhika who served us today with free goodies.  We health care providers really appreciate this. Once again  thank you.
Like any other McDonalds always busy . Shifty customers service. They dont have special limited time items ever they r always out of waffle fries.
Went on busy night, employees was handling everything very great. I dont know the name of the lady working as a supervisor in the front was very helpful and doing her best.
Service was excellent and the burgers were made perfectly not messy and falling apart, fries and coffee fresh! Staff friendly!
Great place staff friendly good atmosphere no waiting
Food came fast at lunch time. Very clean with friendly staff. This is walking in, not the drive through, God help anyone stuck back there.
Always a great quick stop to get food at the drive-in. The order accuracy is good and staff are friendly and kind.
We went to drive through so good service and fast
Its for the times you want something you know you shouldnt but you do it anyways and  you feel guilty right after. My next review will probably be a gym. Get some.
Great coffee   for a great price. The rewards program, where you collect stickers that are on each cup and save them on a card   that is also on each cup, makes it easy to earn free coffee  .
Food is great but this is the second time they  supposed to put large items which I paid but end up receiving medium
Staff was polite and they allowed last minute entry at closure time.
Do you need somewhere to go to bring your kids to a nice dine in, or take out meal?! Well  McDonalds is the place to go. Good food and fast too.
Its McDonalds what else is there to say dollar drink days are still going on thats good.
It was actually pretty good. Very nice staff and follow COVID 19 instructions. I had great visit.
This is the best McDonalds around, not once have they screwed up my order.
Nice place to go for lunch!!
I love the experience and employees. They are very fast and incredible.
Wonderful and fast service. Staff is really nice especially Jatin. He is very friendly and nice person.
Tasty chicken sandwich and fries. Made fresh. Fast service
Mmmm chicken Big Mac wit the sauce mmmmmmmm
Was served by someone named Pragya, Nice service and super fast too.
It was great to see the staff friendly and food was very freshly prepared and served
Always Fast and friendly service here! Good team work here. Thank you.
The staff is very friendly.
Their coffee is great. Thats why I go, because they use the old timmies coffee supplier. :)
I like this place! I come here all the time...they are the reason Im broke LOL
There vety non judgemental here and seem to treat every person the same i liked that factor alot
Very impressive environment and really good staff and if you visit be sure to have mc chicken spicy habanero and mcflurry
Great service, never had service like this. Amazing, so impressed

Its great, theres fast service and you can order online.
Highly recommended
1st class dining. Even Umberto stopped at our table and chatted!
Very good customer service manager saagar was very kind to us,made our day
Very fast service. Good food. Drive-thru.
One of the best mcdonads in Surrey
I strongly appreciate the staff speed and hospitality  thank you for your hard work!
Quick drive thru experience
Excellent service . Very good quality of food fresh and yummy.
The best its ever been. It must be under new management or something. Im very impressed.
Great customer service

Quick and professional service. Thank you Food

Good service

easy on the road trip.. you can always have them
